      "docs": "Output of the mechanized fixpoint resolver (D2). Each variant names the one phase the orchestrator must execute next to move toward convergence: RunDfp (dry gate open), RunRfp { scopes } (one or more review scopes are open), RunRefVerify (ref-verify gate open), Commit (all gates green; safe to commit). scopes is a non-empty ReviewScopeSet of opaque orchestrator-assigned review-group labels; the domain validates only non-emptiness, not review-group naming.",
