      "module_path": "dry_check",
      "docs": "SHA-256 fingerprint (64-char lowercase hex string) over all dry-check.json fields that affect dry write semantics: threshold, max_parallelism, fast_reasoning_effort, final_reasoning_effort, known_bad_injection_rate_percent, known_bad_detection_threshold_percent. Written into the coverage manifest by dry write; compared by dry check-approved against the current config. A mismatch means the config changed and coverage must be regenerated (Blocked). The all-zeros sentinel (fail_closed()) is written on failed runs so check_approved returns Blocked regardless of current config.",
